en_158292_0	President Maithripala Sirisena stated that it is the responsibility of the government to ensure that the Youth don’t take weapons.
en_158292_1	This was joining the closing ceremony of Yowunpura – the National Youth Ceremony in Trincomalee yesterday.
en_158292_2	Nearly 6,000 youth including foreign participants took part in the ceremony.
en_158292_3	Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe also joined the event.
en_158292_4	President Maithripala Sirisena addressing the event stated that it is the responsibility of the rulers of the country to handover the task of building the country to the Youth.
en_158292_5	President Maithripala Sirisena yesterday engaged in an inspection tour of the Kinniya Base Hospital.
en_158292_6	A protest was being held demanding the hospital be renovated and the President responded positively.
